lead_paragraph: Usain Bolt is set to race in Australia for the first time in his career after it was confirmed the nine-times Olympic gold medalist will take part in the inaugural edition of the Nitro Summer Series in February.

headline.print_headline: Bolt Set to Race in Australia for the First Time
